    "description": "<p>Active Global Home &amp; Community Care is a provider of holistic, professional and affordable eldercare services. &nbsp;Started in 2012 by providing live-in caregivers for elderly with complex medical conditions such as dementia, stroke etc., it has extended to subsidised home care services such as home personal care, home medical, home therapy, home nursing etc. &nbsp;Appointed by the Ministry of Health in 2018, it also operates two active ageing hubs. &nbsp;It has served high quality care to more than 3,000 clients regionally.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
